                                     Overview
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

GoodSync synchronizes and backs up files such as photos, financial documents, 
MP3s, e-mails between desktops, laptops, servers, and external drives.

GoodSync is the latest software in a series of highly reliable, easy-to-use 
products from Siber Systems, the makers of RoboForm. It uses an innovative 
synchronization algorithm that offers true bi-directional synchronization.

See for yourself how easy it is to set up and use GoodSync. Below you will find 
our quick setup guide and how to automate synchronization.


Synchronize Files

  GoodSync syncs files between your computer, mobile devices, FTP, SFTP, Amazon S3,
  Google Drive, SkyDrive, WebDAV, Azure.


Backup Files

  One way sync is your regular backup and GoodSync does it locally, to mobile 
  devices or all the above cloud services.


Direct P2P Sync

  GoodSync Connect sync files between your computers directly, without slowdown 
  introduced by 3rd party servers.


Speed and Real-Time Sync

  GoodSync is very fast and it can sync files on your command, on timer, by 
  schedule or at Real-Time (On File Change).
